ames: Live on BBC in 2022; highlights on QUEST plus live coverage of swimming and diving events\n* World University Games: Live on Eurosport and Olympic Channel\n* Youth Olympics: Highlights on BBC\n* European Games: Live on BBC\n* European Championships (multi-sport event): Live on BBC\n* NCAA: Live coverage and highlights on BBC\n* Invictus Games: Live on BBC\n*Abu Dhabi Grand Slam: Live on Fight Network (UK)\n\n===Radio===\n*Olympic Games: Live on BBC Radio 5 Live until 2024\n*Paralympic Games: Live on BBC Radio 5 Live and BBC Radio 5 Live Sports Extra\n*European Championships (multi-sport event): Live on BBC Radio 5 Live\n\n==Athletics==\n\n===Television===\n* UK Athletics major events: Live on BBC until 2020\n* London Marathon: Live on BBC until 2021\n* Great North Run: Live on BBC in 2019\n* Great Manchester Run: Live on BBC\n* Great South Run: Live on Channel 5\n* Great Scottish Run: Live on BBC\n* Cardiff Half Marathon: Live on BBC\n* Great North Run: Live on BBC\n* Brighton Marathon: Highlights on Channel 4\n* Manchester Marathon: Highlights on Channel 4\n* Manchester Half-Marathon: Highlights on Channel 4\n* Yorkshire Marathon: Highlights on Channel 4\n* British Athletics - Indoor Championships: Live on BBC\n* IAAF World Championships in Athletics: Live on BBC until 2023\n* IAAF World Indoor Championships in Athletics: Live on BBC until 2023\n* IAAF World Cross Country Championships: Live on BBC until 2023\n* IAAF Diamond League: All international meetings live; 2 UK meetings live until 2020 with highlights of all meetings on BBC until 2023\n* IAAF World Relays: Live on BBC until 2023\n* IAAF Continental Cup: Live on BBC until 2023\n* Athletics World Cup: Live on Sky Sports in 2018\n* European Athletics Championships: Live on BBC, QUEST and Eurosport until 2018\n* European Team Championships: Live on BBC\n* European Athletics Indoor Championships: Live on BBC\n* European Cross Country Championships: Live on BBC\n* European Athletics Junior Championships: L