e Derby]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racecoursemediagroup.com/news/bbc-radio-5-live-signs-new-deal-with-racecourse-media-group/ |title=BBC Radio 5 live signs new deal with Racecourse Media Group  |date=18 February 2013 |accessdate=3 July 2013}}</ref>\n\n*[[BBC World Service]]\n[[BBC Radio 5 Live|5 Live]] commentary on [[The Grand National]]\n\n*[[Talksport]]\nCommentary on major meetings including [[Cheltenham Festival]], [[The Grand National]], [[Royal Ascot]] and [[The Derby]] on [[Talksport]] and [[Talksport|Talksport 2]]\n\n==Equestrianism==\n\n===Television===\n*[[Horse of the Year Show]]: Highlights on BBC Sport\n*[[Royal International Horse Show]]: Live on BBC Sport\n*[[British Jumping Derby|Hickstead Derby]]: Highlights on BBC Sport\n*[[Olympia Horse Show]]: Live on BBC Sport and QUEST\n*[[International Federation for Equestrian Sports|Global Champions Tour]]: Live coverage of London event on BBC and QUEST\n*[[Badminton Horse Trials]]: Live on BBC Sport until 2020<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2016/badminton-rights|title=BBC and Badminton Horse Trials extend rights until 2020 |publisher=BBC }}</ref>\n*[[Burghley Horse Trials]]: Live on BBC Sport\n*[[World Equestrian Games]]: Live on BBC Sport\n\n==Darts==\n\n===Television===\n*[[PDC World Darts Championship]]: Live on [[Sky Sports]] until 2025<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skysports.com/darts/news/12288/11169250/darts-to-remain-on-sky-sports-after-new-seven-year-deal|title=Darts to remain on Sky Sports after new seven-year deal}}</ref>\n*[[Premier League Darts|Premier League]]: Live on [[Sky Sports]] until 2025\n*[[Grand Slam of Darts]]: Live on [[Sky Sports]] until 2025\n*[[World Matchplay (darts)|World Matchplay]]: Live on [[Sky Sports]] until 2025\n*[[World Grand Prix (darts)|World Grand Prix]]: Live on [[Sky Sports]] until 2025\n*[[World Cup of Darts]] Live on [[Sky Sports]] until 2025\n* UK Open: Live on ITV4 until 2020\n* European Championship: Live on ITV4 until 20